---
layout : base.njk
title : Teen Fit - North
coach:
    name: Ali Sensintaffar
    email: asensintaffar@swimmaccarolina.org
---

{% banner title, {image: 'teen-fit.jpg'} %}

<main id="main" class="bg-gray-100 py-6">
    <div class="container overflow-hidden">
        <p>
            <a href="/">Home</a> /
            <a href="/teen-fit/">Teen Fit</a> /
            {{ title }}
        </p>

        <p class="lead">
            SwimMAC's Middle School Teen Fit (MSTF) or High School Teen Fit (HSTF) offers a chance for your child to improve
            technique in all 4 strokes with individual attention from highly qualified coaches, gain endurance & strength, and have
            fun with swimming! Whether you are looking for a fitness activity, preparing for a school swim team, getting ready for
            summer league, or cross training for other sports, swimming is a great way to stay active and get stronger.
        </p>

        <div class="card p-4">
            <h2>Overview</h2>

            <ul>
                <li>Swim 100 yards of freestyle and 100 yards of backstroke
                <li>Some knowledge of breaststroke and butterfly</li>
            </ul>

        </div>

        <div class="card p-4 my-6">
            <div class="text-right">
                <a href="https://app3.jackrabbitclass.com/portal/ppLogin.asp?id=541680" class="button button--small mb-3" target="_blank">Portal Login</a>
            </div>

            <h3 class="separator-center">Bridge Program Clinics Calendar</h3>
            <p class="text-center">Clinics are available to swimmers aged 6-17 who can swim 25 yards (1 lap) of all four strokes without stopping or pulling on lane lines</p>
            <div class="my-8 mx-auto" style="max-width: 800px;">
                <iframe src="https://app3.jackrabbitclass.com/eventcalendar.asp?orgid=541680" width="100%" height="650" scrolling="yes" class="iframe-class" frameborder="0"></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-4 my-6">
            <h3 class="separator-center">Schedule and Registration for Teen Fit North</h3>

            {% if jackrabbit.teenFitNorth.sessions.length > 0 %}
                {% for session in jackrabbit.teenFitNorth.sessions %}
                <h3 class="separator-left mt-12">{{ session.session }}</h3>
                <p>There is an additional annual registration fee of $30, which includes swim cap and t-shirt.</p>

                <script src="https://app.jackrabbitclass.com/jr3.0/Openings/OpeningsJS?OrgID={{ jackrabbit.teenFitNorth.orgId }}&amp;Session={{ session.session }}&showCols=location,Cat1&hidecols=Class,Gender,Session,ages&style=font-size:16px&sort=days" type="text/javascript"></script>
                {% endfor %}
            {% else %}
                <div class="bg-red-100 border border-red-900 p-4 my-6">
                    There are no scheduled Teen Fit classes at this time
                </div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="card p-4 my-6">
            {% coachContact coach.name, coach.email %}
        </div>

        <div class="card p-4 my-6">
            {% include 'hffa-map.njk' %}
        </div>
    </div>

</main>